io.spine.tools.protoc.plugin

Class ClassMember

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.tools.protoc.plugin.AbstractCompilerOutput
      • io.spine.tools.protoc.plugin.ClassMember
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompilerOutput

    public final class ClassMember
extends AbstractCompilerOutput
    A compiler output which alters a generated message with an additional method or nested type.

    The output is added on the class_scope insertion point.
